Heavily Modded version of Knas_Speedcastle (map by RunE)
Majority of the walls are glass with the floors solid
All of the crates bust with two easter eggs
Glass walls cannot be shot through

This is a beta release, I am having trouble with the vvis.exe hanging up when run in normal mode,
so this version is vvis.exe fast mode. The lighting is a little of due to the compile method. 


ENJOY!!!
